    },

    "star_mesh": {
      "_comment": "LOD 2 close-range mesh tunables. core_radius_scale: visual core sphere size relative to StarRecord.radius. atmosphere_*_scale: outer plasma layers (always > 1.0). corona_scale: additive halo billboard size relative to radius. surface_*: noise/animation parameters for the plasma surface shader. corona_*: corona shader falloff and intensity. light_attenuation: OmniLight3D attenuation curve (1.0 = inverse-square).",
